_sText:
I have played deathrun about four weeks now and for one week ago I decied to build my one deathrun map.

This map have three levels with ca.10 traps each, total 30 traps.
The map have a maximum of 64 players for maximal deathrun madness xD.

Big thanks to Lemonpie who helped me alot with beta testing and finding bugs and misses in the level designe.

theam
* smoth and dev/dev

features
* 3 levels
* 30 traps
* 64 spawnpoints (2 t spawnpoints and 62 ct spawnpoints)
* dev.dev testure
* smoth lines and shapes
* included .nav file 

Special thanks
* lemonpie ( for beta testing )
* me ( for the creation of this map xD )

I hope you like this map and have fun with playing it!
please rate and leave a comment! 

/M4A1|a12 killingspree
